text.tspan: Hickory is a very crafty mouse who likes to invent
gadgets, gizmos, and perform all sorts of other
shenanigans. His pride and joy is a walking grandfather
clock automaton that he built all by himself. Hickory
never stops talking about how much time he saves by
traveling around the mansion using the robot, which he
has named Dickory, instead of his own two feet.
Apparently he’s making a Dickory Mk. II, but he
refuses to share any information about it. In his spare
time he likes to watch mouse soap operas, which I
didn’t know existed until gathering info for this
document. He’s interesting, and definitely fun to
talk to.
Hickory
The Engineer
Age: 4
Species: Mouse
Alignment: Good
Hickory inside Dickory
he stole my camera >:|
